##Meet-up moments:

After 1 hour: Quick sync to make sure interfaces match
After 3 hours: Integration party - wire everything together
Final hour: Add memes, test with hilarious data, practice your demo


##Pro Tips for This Specific Project

Person 1: Seed at least 3-4 weird tables with different data types. Think: timestamps, JSONs, arrays - give the agents ammo
Person 2: Test your prompts early! The agents should escalate from simple SELECTs to absolute mayhem by round 5
Person 3: Streamlit has st.empty() for live updates - use it to make queries appear in real-time like a chat feed

##The Demo Script
When you present, have Person 3 drive:

